            <h1 class="cd-text cd-title">stickers</h1>
            <p class="cd-text">Stickers are used for promotional information such as discounts or to highlight a feature. Often they are positioned absolutely over an image or other element. They are suitable for use in <a href="features">feature blocks</a> or <a href="page-sections">page sections</a></p>

            <h2 class="cd-text cd-title">colours</h2>

